parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tailgate cables can cause the tailgate to fall suddenly, potentially leading to injuries or accidents.
symptoms: The tailgate cables break or corrode
causing the tailgate to fall or drop unexpectedly
often when someone is sitting or standing on it.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent ABS Light and Brake Light Illumination
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent illumination of the ABS and brake lights can cause confusion and distraction for the driver, potentially leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: ABS light and brake light on the instrument panel come on intermittently
sometimes immediately after starting the vehicle
and may reset after turning off the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause extended stopping distances, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: ABS engages at slow speeds
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brakes make a grinding noise
vehicle pulls to one side
and ABS light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature brake wear and corrosion can lead to reduced braking performance, increased stopping distances, and accidents.
symptoms: Brake rotors and pads wear out prematurely
brakes make a scraping noise
and corrosion is visible on brake components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the parking brake can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The parking brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the parking brake does not hold
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the radiator can cause coolant leaks, overheating, and engine damage, leading to costly repairs and potential accidents.
symptoms: The radiator leaks coolant
the radiator has rust or corrosion
the engine overheats
the radiator fluid reservoir is clogged with rust.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drive train can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle makes a whining noise
the drive shaft twists or breaks
the transmission slips or fails
the vehicle stalls or loses power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The transmission slips or fails
the vehicle loses power or acceleration
the transmission shifts unexpectedly
the vehicle stalls or hesitates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause difficulty shifting gears, loss of vehicle control, and accidents.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch does not engage or disengage properly
the vehicle is difficult to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drive shaft can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The drive shaft shakes or vibrates violently
the drive shaft twists or breaks
the vehicle loses power or acceleration.
